trans-unit.source: Contains information that enables a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Binding" /> to resolve a data binding to either the property of an object or the property of the current object in a list of objects.
trans-unit.target: Contém informações que permitem que um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Binding" /> resolva uma associação de dados para a propriedade de um objeto ou a propriedade do objeto atual em uma lista de objetos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> is returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.BindingMemberInfo%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> class.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> é retornado pelo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.BindingMemberInfo%2A> propriedade o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> classe.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> is created from the string passed to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> é criada a partir de cadeia de caracteres passada para o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> construtor.

trans-unit.source: The following code example prints the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> for each control on a form.
trans-unit.target: O código a seguir exemplo imprime o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> para cada controle em um formulário.

trans-unit.source: A navigation path that resolves to either the property of an object or the property of the current object in a list of objects.
trans-unit.target: Um caminho de navegação que resolve para a propriedade de um objeto ou para a propriedade do objeto atual em uma lista de objetos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" />.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> is created automatically when you call the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> constructor with a control-property name, data source, and navigation path.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> é criada automaticamente quando você chama o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> construtor com um nome de propriedade de controle, a fonte de dados e o caminho de navegação.

trans-unit.source: The `dataMember` parameter contains the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> string.
trans-unit.target: O `dataMember` parâmetro contém o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> cadeia de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: Gets the property name of the data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome da propriedade do objeto associado a dados.

trans-unit.source: The property name of the data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: O nome da propriedade do objeto associado a dados.

trans-unit.source: This can be an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Isso pode ser uma cadeia de caracteres vazia ("").

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> is the last item found in the navigation path returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> é o último item encontrado no caminho de navegação retornado pelo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: For example, if a new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> is created that has a `dataMember` parameter of "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate", <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> will return "OrderDate".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se um novo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> é criado e tem um `dataMember` parâmetro de "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate" <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> retornará "OrderDate".

trans-unit.source: The following code example gets the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> of each <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> on a form, and prints the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property values of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.
trans-unit.target: O código a seguir exemplo obtém o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> de cada <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> em um formulário e imprime o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> valores de propriedade de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the information that is used to specify the property name of the data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém as informações que são usadas para especificar o nome da propriedade do objeto associado a dados.

trans-unit.source: An empty string (""), a single property name, or a hierarchy of period-delimited property names that resolves to the property name of the final data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres vazia (""), um nome de propriedade única, ou uma hierarquia de nomes de propriedade delimitados que resolve para o nome da propriedade do objeto de associação de dados final.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> is created automatically when you call the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> constructor with a control-property name, data source, and navigation path.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> é criada automaticamente quando você chama o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> construtor com um nome de propriedade de controle, a fonte de dados e o caminho de navegação.

trans-unit.source: The `dataMember` parameter contains the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> string.
trans-unit.target: O `dataMember` parâmetro contém o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> cadeia de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> is the period delimitated combination of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> values.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> é a combinação de delimitated Períoda do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> valores.

trans-unit.source: For example, when a new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> is created by using a `dataMember` parameter of "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate", <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> will return "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, quando um novo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> é criado usando um `dataMember` parâmetro de "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate" <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> retornará "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate".

trans-unit.source: The following code example gets the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> object of each <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> on a form, and prints the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property values of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.
trans-unit.target: O código a seguir exemplo obtém o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> objeto de cada <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> em um formulário e imprime o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> valores de propriedade de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the property name, or the period-delimited hierarchy of property names, that comes before the property name of the data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome da propriedade ou a hierarquia de nomes de propriedade delimitados por período, que antecede o nome da propriedade do objeto associado a dados.

trans-unit.source: The property name, or the period-delimited hierarchy of property names, that comes before the data-bound object property name.
trans-unit.target: O nome da propriedade, ou a hierarquia de nomes de propriedade, delimitados que antecede o nome da propriedade de objeto associado a dados.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> is the period delimitated combination of property names that comes before the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> in the navigational path returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> é o período de combinação separada da propriedade nomes que antecede o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> no caminho de navegação retornado pelo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: For example, when a new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> is created that has a `dataMember` parameter of "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate", <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> will return "Customers.custToOrders".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, quando um novo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> é criado e tem um `dataMember` parâmetro de "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate" <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> retornará "Customers.custToOrders".

trans-unit.source: The following code example gets the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> of each <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> on a form, and prints the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property values of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.
trans-unit.target: O código a seguir exemplo obtém o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> de cada <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> em um formulário e imprime o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> valores de propriedade de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified object is equal to this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o objeto especificado é igual a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="otherObject" /> is a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" /> and both <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember" /> strings are equal; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="otherObject" /> for um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" /> e as duas cadeias de caracteres <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember" /> forem iguais, caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> strings are compared with a culture setting of <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> cadeias de caracteres são comparadas com uma configuração de cultura <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A>.
